node.text: So many people ask me about my tattoos. I've got Florida repped to the fullest, but it goes deeper than that.  @shopmadrabbit and I had some fun talking sleeves, tattoo aftercare, mindfulness, and the importance of creativity.  Check it out and let me know what tattoo I should get next? #bebold  #madrabbitpartner

node.title: Caeleb Dressel Spilling Ink with Mad Rabbit

node.text:
Hey guys…it’s giveaway time!🦅

ISL launched their platform www.isl.global where you can subscribe to watch the ISL Season 3 online and I am giving away 20 FREE subscriptions to this platform!

To become one of the lucky 20, all you have to do is:

1️⃣ Follow me

2️⃣ Follow @iswimleague

3️⃣ Like this post

4️⃣ Tag at least two friends in the comments below

This contest will take place from 17 to 23 September

Winners will be chosen randomly

‼️But wait, there’s more‼️

To increase your chances of becoming a WINNER you can also take part in a SPECIAL draw over at @iswimleague 

The main prize is a trip for 2 people to the Grand Final of the ISL Season 3 🔥

Enter to win NOW!

Good luck and Go Dors 🦅
